-testing priority
1. high value features --- the most important features in your app. like viewing and buying a product 
2. edge cases in high value features --- like adding 1000 items in the cart
3. things that are easy to break
4. basic react component testing
   -user interactions
   - conditional rendering
   - utils / hooks
   
   
   
